      "text": "みんな、部屋は決まったか？　それじゃあルームキーを\n配るぞ。……ん？　すず、どうかしたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "みんな、部屋は決まったか？　それじゃあルームキーを\n配るぞ。……ん？　すず、どうかしたのか？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.3731289506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
